Ionian OS Installation Manual
=============================
Virtualbox VDI installation
---------------------------
amd64 and i386 follow the same installation process.  
1) Download the Ionian vdi version from http://download/ioncoin.org/Ionian  
2) Unzip the vdi file that you have just downloaded  
3) Create a new Virtual Machine in Oracle Virtualbox   
4) Select your downloaded VDI when asked to enter 
